The &#39;max-link-hops&#39; value for the &#39;classic&#39; scopes (BroadScope, 
DomainScope, HostScope, PathScope) only counts plain navigation-link 
&#39;L&#39; hops.

So in each of your cases, there are only 8 &#39;L&#39;s, and the 
&#39;max-link-hops&#39; has not been exceeded.

Hope this helps,

- Gordon @ IA

